upture totale au nom du changement global).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aAesthetics, Canadian. 0aFrench-Canadian poetryy20th centuryxHistory and criticismxTheory, etc. 0aFrench-Canadian poetryzQuébec (Province)xHistory and criticismxTheory, etc. 0aPoeticsxHistoryy20th century. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020z978311127473740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763747651?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763747651423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763747651/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-127473-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles